100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/20e77/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 188w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/f21ed/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 375w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/88df8/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" srcSet=\"/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/20e77/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 188w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/f21ed/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 375w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/88df8/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 750w\" src=\"/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/88df8/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg\" alt=\"A thank you to The PM Group employee Elizabeth Bomes\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/20e77/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 188w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/f21ed/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 375w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/88df8/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" srcset=\"/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/20e77/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 188w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/f21ed/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 375w,\n/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/88df8/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 750w\" src=\"/static/952381f769dea34eea5e14aa5c5f9423/88df8/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg\" alt=\"A thank you to The PM Group employee Elizabeth Bomes\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Like the song says&#8230;&#8221;<em>we never can say goodbye</em>” when we lose someone like Elizabeth Bomer! She is headed off to the land of special events, lavish galas, ornate birthday parties…but most importantly she will be a part owner of her new employer.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We will miss you Elizabeth and we wish you all the best in your new endeavors. We thank you for the new business you brought to the agency and your hard work and dedication you showed as a part of our team. You can certainly say you contributed to The PM Group being San Antonio’s largest marketing and advertising agency!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>All the best and we look forward to working with you again!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Bob Wills</p>\n<p>CEO | Founder</p>\n","title":"We Never Can Say Goodbye…No, No, No No No!","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"We Never Can Say Goodbye…No, No, No No No!","url":"/we-never-can-say-goodbye/"}],"title":"We Never Can Say Goodbye…No, No, No No No! | The PM Group","metaDesc":"The PM Group thanks Elizabeth Bomer for her hard work and dedication to our team as she moves on to a new a new position.","focuskw":"Elizabeth Bomer","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"We Never Can Say Goodbye…No, No, No No No! | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"The PM Group thanks Elizabeth Bomer for her hard work and dedication to our team as she moves on to a new a new position.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"A thank you to The PM Group employee Elizabeth Bomes","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves-300x158.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-5.3.21-Elizabeth-Leaves.jpg 750w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/